Tricia - Stratford - 28

Alex isn't good at this game when playing as the monster.

Tim claimed to be a tanner and Travis claimed to be a troublemaker. The group decided to kill Alex on the off chance he had grabbed a werewolf from the middle, but he had pulled the Tanner and won.

Everybody lied!!! Tim dopplegangered the Tanner from pixels. He lied and said he was the seer and saw pixels' minion. Alex robbed a werewolf from Travis, but lied and said he had robbed pixels' drunk after Tricia (the other werewolf) claimed to have robbed Tim's seer. We killed Travis and Tim, so Tim as the dopple-tanner won, and the Tanner win trumps a werewolf win, so even though Alex and Tricia were alive, they did not win.

Alex was the minion. Travis robbed the hunter from pixels, and then Tim troublemakered the hunter and the minion, so Alex ended with the hunter and Travis with the minion. Alex admitted to being the minion and outed Tricia as the werewolf. 3 shot Alex, now the hunter, who shot Tricia, the real werewolf.
Travis was a solo mason and claimed that, then Tricia (werewolves with Tim) claimed that she and Tim were masons. Tricia and Travis ended up being killed, so the werewolves lost.
Pixels did quite a good job making himself suspicious as the tanner. We killed both him and Tricia, who was a werewolf.
Alex and Travis were werewolves. Evan was being really suspicious, so they were able to throw the blame on him, and we unanimously voted to kill Evan.

Alex was the robber, and switched with Travis, becoming a werewolf. Evan then switched Alex and Travis as the troublemaker, which came out toward the end of the game. Alex had lied during the game, saying he switched with Tim, since he thought he was a werewolf. But, since he and Travis were switched back, Alex was the robber again.

Tim and Tricia were both werewolves. Tricia convinced us she was the trouble maker. Evan was the hunter while Alex was the drunk and didn't know what he was. 2 votes killed Alex, 2 votes killed Evan. Because Evan was the hunter, he was pointing at Travis, so Travis died. All villagers are dead.

We found the paranoid solider very early on. This caused Joe to become lost, which caused a lot of issues because he had relationships with the medic and the virologist, both of which were in play. We were able to eradicate black. We were very close to winning and curing yellow, but we hit an epidemic that ended up outbreaking in San Francisco, that hadn't had issues the whole game, and that killed us.

We won August, though it was a rough one. We got some epidemics early on, and weren't able to find the immunologist before they got away. Some nasty chain outbreaks at the end from San Francisco to Chicago, and then Chicago outward have now turned Atlanta into a Faded city. We were able to still eradicate blue.

We won July! Pixels found the virologist completely on his first turn. We thought we could end the game on Tricia's turn, but it turns out we needed a 5th action. Had to go one round around making sure we didn't die to bide our time to get back to Tricia. Eradicated blue.

We won June! Got a little unlucky at the end. Made sure for Tricia to end in Washington in order to give Pixels the final blue to win the game. Then an epidemic happened, Washington got 3 cubes, and then was infected, giving her a scar.

We won May! Only blue left to cure. Alex discards Essen card to fly there. Pixels (rivals with Alex) discards two cards to pick up the Essen card. On his turn, Pixels discards Essen to fly to Essen. Alex then discards two cards to get Essen back, as he is already sitting in Essen. Pixels then moves to London, as he has a London card. Sam needs two more blue cards to cure blue. She moves to Essen, gets Alex's card, moves to London, and gets Pixel's card. Bam.
We won April! We eradicated black. Also started to get faded cities. Tokyo was the first to get faded people, and it immediately outbroke.
We won March! And we eradicated black.
March. Lost, red blew up. Should have had about 4 more outbreaks, but we ran out of red cubes.
We won February! Also we eradicated black.
We won January! Also we were able to eradicate blue.
